1808年，英国开始印度{{Link-en|大三角勘察|Great Trigonometric Survey}}，勘測队在19世纪30年代到达了喜马拉雅山丘陵地带。尼泊尔担心英国借机侵略，拒绝英国勘測队进入尼泊尔。<ref name="Gillman2000">{{cite book|editor=Peter Gillman| others=assisted by Leni Gillman| title=''Everest: Eighty Years of Triumph and Tragedy''| year=2000| location = Seattle, WA | publisher=Mountaineers|
